"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-08-10-australia-put-a-unique-spin-on-breakdancing-at-the-olympics-leading-to-disappointing-ridicule\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rachael Gunn, a 36-year-old\\u00c2 lecturer at Macquarie University in Sydney, delivered a historic display at the ParisOlympics, representing Australia as their first competing breakdancer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999351985, \"rank\": 6.451588634250744e-11, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999317556960122, \"rank\": 4.7615542166538516e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.510069089812037e-20, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999968684063709, \"rank\": 2.567344756359714e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9971470992336584, \"rank\": 0.001563621654271395, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 36-year-old\\u00c2 lecturer\", \"from\": 14, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic display\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 101}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"their first competing breakdancer\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And although Gunn (AKA \\\"Raygun\\\") lost all three of her group matches, she stole the show regardless.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999317556960122, \"rank\": 4.7615542166538516e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AKA \\\"Raygun\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"her group matches\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Displaying a series of moves that could easily be mistaken as performance art, people on social media seemed to have a great deal of fun sharing clips of her at the games\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 referring to her in action as being \\\"possessed by the spirit of Julia Stiles in 'Save the Last Dance'\\\" as she debuted a maneuver now being referred to as \\\"the kangaroo\\\"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 which Gunn herself took in stride, although Anna Meares,\\u00c2 Australian two-time Olympic cycling gold medallist, viewed the reception as\\u00c2 \\\"really disappointing.\\\"\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Stiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Julia Stiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Stiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_Stiles\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999317556960122, \"rank\": 4.7615542166538516e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9985115899013913, \"rank\": 0.0014740150397202212, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"moves\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"performance art\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"a great deal\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"fun sharing clips\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Dance\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"a maneuver\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"the kangaroo\\\"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"stride\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"the reception\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a quote obtained fromThe Guardian, Gunn comments on what could be seen as trolling for her unique breakdancing and costume choice\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 which some said resembled a fast food worker's uniform\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 saying,\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAll my moves are original.\\u00c2 Creativity is really important to me.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a quote\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"her unique breakdancing\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"costume\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast food worker's uniform\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Creativity\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out there and I show my artistry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my artistry\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there is certainly no doubt about that.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympic breakdancer Rachael Gunn has a PhD in breakdancing and dance culture.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9985115899013913, \"rank\": 0.0014740150397202212, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999351985, \"rank\": 6.451588634250744e-11, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999317556960122, \"rank\": 4.7615542166538516e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a PhD\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"breakdancing and dance culture\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAll my moves are original,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she told reporters after her performance.pic.twitter.com/8to8quMx9y \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Michael Nayna (@MikeNayna)August 10, 2024 \\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 the dynamic and the power moves\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 so I wanted to move differently\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 be artistic and creative\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 because how many chances do you get in a lifetime to do that on an international stage?\\\"\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my moves\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance.pic.twitter.com/8to8quMx9y\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"these girls\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"best\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the dynamic\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"differently\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"creative\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"how many chances\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"an international stage\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said this week toBBC Sport.\\u00c2 \\\"I was always the underdog and wanted to make my mark in a different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999317556960122, \"rank\": 4.7615542166538516e-05, \"text\":